comment: Zipser (CHI) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Joseph (TOR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Patterson (TOR) makes marginal contact with Butler (CHI) that does not affect his SQBR.
Tucker (TOR) sets the screen on Butler (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The two players briefly engage and separate following the screen.
Lauvergne (CHI) maintains legal guarding positon and makes incidental contact with DeRozan (TOR) that does not affect his SQBR.
Butler (CHI) gathers the ball with his left foot on the floor and takes three steps prior to his shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) makes incidental contact with Butler (CHI) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Rondo (CHI) maintains legal guarding position on Joseph's (TOR) drive to the basket and post up.
RHH shows that Rondo (CHI) does not step out of bounds prior to making contact with the ball.
Valentine (CHI) makes contact to DeRozan (TOR) after the gather that affects his driving shot attempt.
Tucker (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Butler (CHI) that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Patterson (TOR) sets the screen on Butler (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Patterson (TOR) makes marginal contact with Butler (CHI) after he secures the loose ball.
Butler (CHI) makes marginal contact with VanVleet (TOR) on the screen.
Rondo (CHI) legally contests DeRozan's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Rondo (CHI) gathers the ball and hops consecutively on the same foot.
Rondo (CHI) and VanVleet (TOR) briefly engage with one another off ball.

Tucker (TOR) makes incidental contact with Butler (CHI) that does not affect his SQBR.

Whitehead (BKN) legally contests Harris' (DET) shot attempt.
